<div class="your-Turn">
  <h4><i class="fa fa-pencil" aria-hidden="true"></i> Your turn</h4>
  <ol>
    <li>Mix a background color you love in the picker and copy its code.</li>
    <li>In your <code>body</code> rule, change the <code>background-color</code> value to your hex code.</li>
    <li>If you go dark, keep your words readable: add <code>color: #f5f5f5;</code> to the body rule too.</li>
    <li>Found a background that feels like you? Click <strong>Check My Work</strong>.</li>
